Being a Blessing is for self empowerment and external development 

Click to edit text


Click to edit text

Mission

Click to edit text

Be The Blessing Foundation (BTB) will bring resources and programs exposing and encouraging opportunity and growth to underrepresented and underprivileged communities, while gradually diminishing the impacts of disparities.
